description: CO2 Gro Inc., together with its subsidiaries, focuses on commercializing patent-licensed CO2 gas infusion technology and patent-pending US PTO CO2 delivery solutions system. The company was formerly known as BlueOcean NutraSciences Inc. and changed its name to CO2 Gro Inc. in April 2018. CO2 Gro Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
